command=grep -n evidence_refresh_flake_smoke cairn/specs/mc-compatibility/spec.md
5369:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.contract] The evidence refresh pass MUST define a bounded smoke set, command scope, runtime limits, evidence paths, and non-claims before running checks.
5373:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.contract.scope]
5381:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.baseline] The evidence refresh pass MUST run selected non-mutating baseline checks before manifest refresh.
5385:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.baseline.recorded]
5392:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.logs] Review-critical smoke output MUST be recorded under `docs/evidence/` with explicit successful exit statuses or blocker notes.
5396:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.logs.reviewable]
5404:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.manifests] BLAKE3 manifests MUST be refreshed only for changed tracked evidence files and rerun to a deterministic fixpoint.
5408:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.manifests.fixpoint]
5416:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.validation] The evidence refresh pass MUST record task-evidence checks, Cairn gates, sync/archive checks, and post-archive validation before closeout.
5420:r[mc_compatibility.evidence_refresh_flake_smoke.validation.logs]
